OL,3,CJail for woman who defrauded pensioner
OL,4,Cout of life savings
OL,6,FA woman from Gloucester has been
OL,7,Fjailed after defrauding her elderly
OL,8,Fneighbour out of his #290,000 life
OL,9,Fsavings.
OL,11,FChelsea Iles exploited her victim - a
OL,12,Fman in his 80s - after assuming caring
OL,13,Fresponsibilities in October 2022.
OL,15,FIn the months that followed, the 29-
OL,16,Fyear-old took control of his bank
OL,17,Faccount and spent #80,000 on gambling
OL,18,Fwebsites.
