OL,3,CJail for woman who defrauded pensioner
OL,4,Cout of life savings
OL,6,FThe court heard the victim lived next
OL,7,Fdoor to Iles' family in the Matson
OL,8,Farea of Gloucester.
OL,10,FIles' mother used to look after the
OL,11,Fvictim, helping him with household
OL,12,Ftasks and buying his food shopping.
OL,14,FTo pay for groceries, she would
OL,15,Fwithdraw small sums of money from his
OL,16,Fbank account using his card and PIN.
OL,18,FWhen Iles' mother died in October
OL,19,F2022, Iles assumed caring
OL,20,Fresponsibilities - and gained access
OL,21,Fto his accounts.
