OL,3,CJail for woman who defrauded pensioner
OL,4,Cout of life savings
OL,6,FThe victim's nephew described their
OL,7,Fordeal as "despicable".
OL,9,F"It has been a very upsetting,
OL,10,Fstressful time for my uncle, wondering
OL,11,Fwhether he will get his money back,"
OL,12,Fhe said.
OL,14,F"He put his trust in the next-door
OL,15,Fneighbour just to do some shopping for
OL,16,Fhim. He couldn't believe that she
OL,17,Fcould do such a despicable thing to
OL,18,Fhim."
